attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles a table. He starts by unscrewing the first leg of the table. After that, the student unscrews the second leg of the table. Once the student unscrews the two first legs he detaches them. To finish the task, the student unscrews and detaches the other two legs.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrews the first leg of the table.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student drops the hex socket head.

attributes.Action sentence: The student detaches the first leg of the table.
The student detaches the second leg of the table.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student drops the allen wrench.
The student drops the Allen wrench.

attributes.Action sentence: The student unscrews the third leg of the table.
The student unscrews the fourth leg of the table.
